    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. While the exterior shows some light signs of use consistent with its age, such as minor paint chips, the overall appearance remains very clean. The interior is comfortable and well-maintained, with all major electronics and climate control systems functioning as they should. Buyers can expect a reliable and pleasant driving experience from this solid, honest car.",
