    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and sparkling clean inside and out. It runs like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You won\u2019t find another one this clean! Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
